    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the point in \"taking care of myself\" when all that does is keep me around to make their lives harder. i look at them and i just feel so guilty. sometimes i wonder if it would actually be more selfless to just... stop. you know? like, to make the decision for them so they don't have to watch me fade away bit by bit. wouldn't that be a more peaceful way for things to go?",
